```python
while True:
    integer = input(&quot; :&quot;)
    try:
        integer = int(integer)
    except ValueError:
        print(&quot;Must enter a number&quot;)
        continue
    if integer &lt; 0:
        print(&quot;Must enter a positive number&quot;)
        continue
    else:
        break
```

